      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just about rebuilding. the core of who i thought i was—the way i perceived reality—was built on a falsehood. how can i even look at the world the same way after this? there is no 'new foundation' when the ground itself was a hallucination. i'm just... empty. there's nothing left to salvage.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
